Next Steps for You:

To connect your auxpery.com.au Stripe account to Guide:

Add the webhook endpoint in your Stripe Dashboard:

Go to Developers → Webhooks → Add endpoint
Webhook URL: You'll need to expose port 8000 externally or set up routing
Events to send: checkout.session.completed, customer.subscription.updated, customer.subscription.deleted, invoice.paid, invoice.payment_failed
Set the webhook signing secret in your Replit Secrets:

Copy the signing secret from Stripe
Add it as STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET in your environment



